## Quick Setup (Copy and Paste)

Run these commands in your TFE directory:

```bash
# Initialize the games submodule
git submodule init games/TUIClassics
git submodule update

# Build the games
cd games/TUIClassics
make build
cd ../..

echo "âœ… TUIClassics installed! Press F9 or click [ðŸŽ®] to launch games."
```

## What This Does

1. **Initializes the submodule**: Links TFE to the TUIClassics repository
2. **Downloads the code**: Clones TUIClassics into `games/TUIClassics/`
3. **Builds the games**: Compiles all games (minesweeper, solitaire, etc.)
4. **Ready to play**: TFE will now find games in `./games/TUIClassics/bin/`

## Manual Steps (if needed)

If you already cloned TFE without `--recursive`, run:

```bash
git submodule update --init --recursive
cd games/TUIClassics && make build
```

